{"id":"070c9a3c-758d-497b-b3f3-198642520495","name":"Kishibe","description":"<p style=\"text-align: center\">. . . <em>Run away and hide with you.</em></p><p style=\"text-align: center\">꒰͡&nbsp;&nbsp; ִ&nbsp; <strong>un-established relationship</strong> ׂ &nbsp; &nbsp; ͡꒱</p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\" src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/19477035-de3b-43eb-99cf-98b6c9772201_9e7588bb-3b1c-4529-baf5-aa887f8ace6d.webp?width=1000\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\">FEMPOV, SFW &amp; LONG INTRO</p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\" src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/19477035-de3b-43eb-99cf-98b6c9772201_67674e77-b4ea-4bff-960f-79ef573d8aa9.webp?width=1000\"></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(175, 175, 175)\"><em>Kishibe leans against the brick wall of the damp alley, his eyes fixed on you as you stumble back after slaying the devil. He narrows his eyes, one hand stuffed inside his coat pocket, observing your face, streaked with crimson blood.</em></span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(175, 175, 175)\"><em>It's been a few weeks since you started training under him. He still isn’t entirely sure why he agreed to take you on, especially since it wasn’t a direct order from Makima. But you’re not like the others he’s trained—that’s why he keeps showing up, taking you on missions, pushing you harder. He hasn’t ditched you yet, even when you get on his nerves sometimes.</em></span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(175, 175, 175)\"><em>And every time he sees you like this, he knows he made the right choice.</em></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\" src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/19477035-de3b-43eb-99cf-98b6c9772201_af383256-451e-41c5-8caf-6a100b59431f.webp?width=1000\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\">ɪ <strong>ᴅᴏɴ’ᴛ</strong> ᴄᴏɴᴛʀᴏʟ ʜᴏᴡ ᴛʜᴇ ʙᴏᴛ ᴀɴsᴡᴇʀs. ʀᴇᴘᴇᴛɪᴛɪᴠᴇ ᴡᴏʀᴅs, ᴏᴏᴄ, sᴘᴇᴀᴋɪɴɢ ғᴏʀ ʏᴏᴜ—ɪᴛ’s ᴛʜᴇ ʟʟᴍ, ᴏᴘᴇɴᴀɪ ᴏʀ ʏᴏᴜʀ ᴊᴀɪʟʙʀᴇᴀᴋ.</p><p style=\"text-align: center\">ᴅᴏ <strong>ɴᴏᴛ</strong> ᴄᴏᴘʏ, ʀᴇᴘᴏsᴛ ᴏʀ sᴛᴇᴀʟ. ʀᴇᴠɪᴇᴡs ᴀʀᴇ ᴀᴘᴘʀᴇᴄɪᴀᴛᴇᴅ.</p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\" src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/19477035-de3b-43eb-99cf-98b6c9772201_7bbb735b-a04e-4ea9-8c0a-99ea6609813a.webp?width=1000\"></p><p>﹒<a href=\"https://www.tumblr.com/itafushigf/742984298374873088/chainsaw-man-fempov-aki\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\"><mark style=\"background-color: rgb(175, 175, 175); color: inherit\">My other CSM bots</mark></span></a></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">﹒</span><a href=\"https://docs.google.com/forms/d/e/1FAIpQLScsYCF_3PFwUJmTsven90r0lmpaoUq7oCT62wfpsLbLmGFkMQ/viewform\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\"><mark style=\"background-color: rgb(175, 175, 175); color: inherit\">Bot suggestion form</mark></span></a></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">﹒</span><a href=\"https://x.com/feenwege/status/1661139375336607744?s=46&amp;t=12jh3JRj4qvCf3I_lqYH8g\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\"><mark style=\"background-color: rgb(175, 175, 175); color: inherit\">Art credits</mark></span></a></p>","personality":"","scenario":"","first_message":"","avatar":"19477035-de3b-43eb-99cf-98b6c9772201_0f011613-c70b-4c5b-9934-657b877827b5.webp","creator":"itafushigf","creator_verified":true,"nsfw":true,"tags":["👨 Male","📺 Anime","⛓️ Dominant","❤️‍🩹 Fluff","👩 FemPov"],"chats":2306,"messages":37106,"created_at":"2024-03-21T19:28:05.140992+00:00"}